RISE ASCII SCENE 6
#############################################################################################################
#                                      RISE Ascii Scene File                                                #
#                                                                                                           #
#   File:           painters.RISEscene                                                                      #
#   Description:    Some of the procedural painters available                                               #
#   Author:         Aravind Krishnaswamy                                                                    #
#   Birthdate:      February 23, 2005                                                                       #
